Title: Jezebels
Writer: Kira Snyder (teleplay by), Margaret Atwood (based on the novel by), Bruce Miller (created for television by)
Actors: Elisabeth Moss, Joseph Fiennes, Yvonne Strahovski, Max Minghella
Plot: While his wife is away, Commander Waterford takes Offred on an excursion outside the walls of Gilead to a den of iniquity where she finds a familiar face.
